<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Your OTP Code</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 400px;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #333;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #666;
        }
        .otp-code {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #333;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .link-button {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .link-button:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Your OTP Code</h1>
        <p>Hello <%= username %>,</p>
        <p>Use the following OTP code to complete your process:</p>
        <div class="otp-code"><%= otp %></div>
        
        <p>If you did not request this, please ignore this email.</p>
        <p>Best regards,<br>Book My adventure</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
